    "text": "\u0db6\u0dd3\u0dbd\ufffd Hot"
  },
  {
    "start": 227.12,
    "end": 228.12,
    "text": "Lola."
  },
  {
    "start": 229.12,
    "end": 231.12,
    "text": "Please, please, Lola."
  },
  {
    "start": 231.12,
    "end": 233.12,
    "text": "There's nothing to talk about, Charlie."
  },
  {
    "start": 233.12,
    "end": 235.12,
    "text": "Like, I can't deny that I have feelings for you, but..."
  },
  {
    "start": 236.12,
    "end": 239.12,
    "text": "I can't be friends with you if you're still talking to Stephanie."
  },
  {
    "start": 239.12,
    "end": 241.12,
    "text": "There's nothing between Stephanie."
  },
  {
    "start": 241.12,
    "end": 245.12,
    "text": "I told her that yesterday after that rubbish she pulled."
  },
  {
    "start": 246.12,
    "end": 248.12,
    "text": "You have to believe me."
  },
  {
    "start": 248.12,
    "end": 251.12,
    "text": "Okay, I don't have to do anything."
  },
  {
    "start": 251.12,
    "end": 254.12,
    "text": "Look, I don't want to ruin our friendship either."
  },
  {
    "start": 254.12,
    "end": 259.12,
    "text": "But if it's a choice between losing you and being with you,"
  },
  {
    "start": 261.12,
    "end": 262.12,
    "text": "I choose you."
  },
  {
    "start": 265.12,
    "end": 266.12,
    "text": "Lola."
  },
  {
    "start": 266.12,
    "end": 268.12,
    "text": "What changed between yesterday and today?"
  },
  {
    "start": 270.12,
    "end": 272.12,
    "text": "It came with my senses."
  },
  {
    "start": 274.12,
    "end": 277.12,
    "text": "Look, I'm scared, Lola."
  },
  {
    "start": 279.12,
    "end": 282.12,
    "text": "I don't know what I would do if I were to lose you."
  },
  {
    "start": 284.12,
    "end": 288.12,
    "text": "With you in my life, it just makes sense."
  },
  {
    "start": 294.12,
    "end": 297.12,
    "text": "I give good luck."
  },
  {
    "start": 299.12,
    "end": 301.12,
    "text": "I buy your clothes."
  },
  {
    "start": 303.12,
    "end": 306.12,
    "text": "I'll cook you dinner too."
  },
  {
    "start": 308.12,
    "end": 311.12,
    "text": "As soon as I get home from work."
  },
  {
    "start": 312.12,
    "end": 314.12,
    "text": "I'm so sorry."
  },
